Description: Feature Ordering by Integrated R square Dependence (FORD) is a variable selection algorithm based on the new measure of dependence: Integrated R2 Dependence Coefficient (IRDC). For more information, see the paper: Azadkia and Roudaki (2025),"A New Measure Of Dependence: Integrated R2" <arXiv:2505.18146>.
